name: TK-570
content:
TK-570 was a stormtrooper of the Galactic Empire.
In 1 ABY TK-570 was part of a stormtrooper unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
TK-570 was a Non-Player Character  in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2009 through 2011.
